{"type":null,"faqId":44890,"title":"唤醒词训练不成功，录音界面一直显示（0/3）","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">请按界面提示进行唤醒词训练，如果 “录音界面一直显示（0/3）”可能是您一直按住了训练界面的麦克风图标。 正确的操作是，点击一次麦克风图标并立刻松开，麦克风图标上会有相应动画提示，此时您就可以开始训练唤醒词了。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">如果在训练的过程中，有训练不通过的时候，此时需要你重新点击下麦克风图标，然后再训练。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":144,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"391","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442409278000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-UL10","visitedTimes":3,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"唤醒词,训练,录音","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}